@startuml 扫描时序图
title 用户发起漏洞扫描

actor 用户 as User
participant 前端 as Frontend
participant API网关 as APIGateway
participant 认证服务 as AuthService
participant 扫描服务 as ScanService
participant RabbitMQ as RabbitMQ
participant CeleryWorker as CeleryWorker
participant Nettacker as Nettacker
participant PostgreSQL as PostgreSQL
participant WebSocket as WebSocket

== 用户认证 ==
User -> Frontend: 点击"发起扫描"
Frontend -> Frontend: 获取JWT Token
Frontend -> APIGateway: POST /api/scans (token, target, type)
APIGateway -> AuthService: 验证Token
AuthService -> PostgreSQL: 查询用户
PostgreSQL --> AuthService: 用户数据
AuthService --> APIGateway: Token有效

== 创建任务 ==
APIGateway -> ScanService: create_scan_task()
ScanService -> PostgreSQL: INSERT scan_tasks
PostgreSQL --> ScanService: task_id
ScanService -> RabbitMQ: 发送任务消息
ScanService --> APIGateway: 202 Accepted
APIGateway --> Frontend: {task_id, status: 'pending'}
Frontend --> User: 任务已创建

== 异步扫描 ==
RabbitMQ -> CeleryWorker: 消费任务
CeleryWorker -> PostgreSQL: UPDATE status='running'
CeleryWorker -> Nettacker: 执行扫描
Nettacker --> CeleryWorker: 漏洞列表
CeleryWorker -> PostgreSQL: INSERT vulnerabilities
CeleryWorker -> PostgreSQL: UPDATE status='completed'
CeleryWorker -> WebSocket: 发送通知
WebSocket -> Frontend: 推送结果
Frontend --> User: 显示扫描结果

@enduml